title: 1. Five things you might not know about me- Lisa from the blog Farmhouse on Boone!
description:
In this first episode of the Simple Farmhouse Life podcast, I'm talking about things you don't know about me and my family. As a full-time content creator, people make a lot of assumptions about us based on a very limited glimpse into our lives. It is time to set the record straight on a lot of these!

Get my free 10 day course on how to start a blog HERE.

Follow along with Farmhouse on Boone:

The blog

The Youtube channel

Instagram

Thanks again for listening and I'll see you in the next episode of the Simple Farmhouse Life podcast.
